Params: Lalala! Lalala! It's me, Lumberjack Nanami! Chopping trees in the snow flurry!
One swing! I sing! This weather makes me so happy!
Ugh... Chopping trees is so boring! They don't stand a chance against my chainsaw!
Eh? Sounds like someone's cutting trees over there, too. Poor fella. I should go say hello!
Is the wind too loud? I'll get a lil' closer then.
Wow! Those hardworkin' fellas sure take choppin' down trees serious. They deserve a present!
But... You guys are slower than molasses... All this time, and you barely but a dent in it! It just takes me a second...
Stand aside. I can get this done in the blink of an eye. Then you fellas can go take a load off.
Hmph! Don't want my help, then forget it! But you brats don't gotta be so rude about it. No present for you!
Brats like you deserve a spanking!
Oh, right! Time to try out my new signature move... Super Supreme Whirlwind Armstrong Chainsaw Annihilation—!
The revving of the chainsaw continues.
Hmm... Guess I'm still worked up about getting hurt.
Uh... Oops... Looks like I need to work on my aim. I cut down half of the trees on the mountain...
—I guess I'll just cut down the rest of them. Should be fun watching these guys struggle with no more trees to cut... Hehehehe!
Oh, it's Lucia. Why does she always gotta interrupt me when I'm busy!
Forget her! I'm having too much fun to stop now!
Namami... we're... running... out of... time...!
